resources.string:
Follow the links below to
        grant the recording and storage permission to this app (App settings);
        configure the default key phrases (Service settings);
        view the Trigger rewrite rules (View Trigger rules) and import them into Kõnele, which allows you to start Kõnele
    and say \"launch speech trigger\" to launch itself with the speech trigger service provided by this app;
    launch Kõnele directly with the speech trigger service (Launch Kõnele with trigger service), either in English or Estonian.
    Note that only the first step is required. The other steps are just demonstrating two
        ways of using the service, in both cases the default key phrase is overridden, and
        once heard, the trigger launches Kõnele with rewrite tables \"Lights\" and \"Lights.Hue\".
